{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-9","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor završetaka kombinacija i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da bi se izgovorio završetak kombinacije <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ou</span>, počinje u ustima u položaju zvuka <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>, zatim polako menja jezik i usne ka položaju <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>. Ovaj prelaz treba da bude glatok, bez prekida između ova dva zvuka. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> se naglašava nešto duže, dok je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span> kratak i lagan, što uzrokuje prirodni prelaz umesto dve različite vokale.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ou</span> je kombinovan sa početnim konsonantima, dobija slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mou</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fou</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">dou</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">kou</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zou</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shou</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shou</span> u različitim dijalektima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Slova</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shōu</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">收</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shóu</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">熟</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shǒu</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">手</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shòu</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">受</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-9"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Lin Yating","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_compound_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":148,"finishTimestamp":170.93},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.78,"dialogue":{"text":"ou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.85,"finishTime":3.73,"dialogue":{"text":"mou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":4.97,"finishTime":5.9,"dialogue":{"text":"fou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.32,"finishTime":8.18,"dialogue":{"text":"dou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.54,"finishTime":10.5,"dialogue":{"text":"kou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":11.85,"finishTime":12.74,"dialogue":{"text":"zou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.17,"finishTime":15.23,"dialogue":{"text":"shou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":16.87,"finishTime":17.84,"dialogue":{"text":"shōu","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":18.68,"finishT